<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<theorem xmlns="Theorem"
         xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance"
         type="Corollary"
         id="Thm_RankFormulaMatrix"
         xsi:schemaLocation="Theorem file:/C:/xampp/htdocs/moodle/mod/msm/NewSchemas/Theorem.xsd">
   <caption>Rank formula</caption>
   <statement.theorem>
      <para>
         <para.body>For a matrix <math>
               <latex>\Mtrx{A}</latex>
            </math> of size <math>
               <latex>(m,n)</latex>
            </math>,
			</para.body>
         <index.glossary>
            <term>rank</term>
            <term>formula for matrices</term>
            <info>
               <info.caption>Rank formula for matrices</info.caption>
               <math.display>
                  <latex>
							
\begin{array}{rcl}
n &amp; = &amp; \Rnk{ \Mtrx{ A } } + \Dim{ \NllSp{ \Mtrx{ A } } } \\
  &amp; = &amp; \Dim{ \RowSp{ \Mtrx{ A } } } + \Dim{ \NllSp{ \Mtrx{ A } } } \\
  &amp; = &amp; \Dim{ \ColSp{ \Mtrx{ A } } } + \Dim{ \NllSp{ \Mtrx{ A } } }
\end{array}

						</latex>
               </math.display>
            </info>
         </index.glossary>
      </para>
      <math.display>
         <latex>
				
\begin{array}{rcl}
n &amp; = &amp; \Rnk{ \Mtrx{ A } } + \Dim{ \NllSp{ \Mtrx{ A } } } \\
  &amp; = &amp; \Dim{ \RowSp{ \Mtrx{ A } } } + \Dim{ \NllSp{ \Mtrx{ A } } } \\
  &amp; = &amp; \Dim{ \ColSp{ \Mtrx{ A } } } + \Dim{ \NllSp{ \Mtrx{ A } } }
\end{array}

			</latex>
      </math.display>
   </statement.theorem>
   <proof type="Proof">
      <proof.block>
         <para>
            <para.body>We proved the first identity when we found a 
			<subordinate>
                  <hot>basis for the null space of a matrix</hot>
                  <crossref>
                     <theorem.ref theoremID="Thm_BasisNullSpace"/>
                     <info>
                        <para>
                           <para.body>Look up this theorem.</para.body>
                        </para>
                     </info>
                  </crossref>
               </subordinate>. Then we 
			<subordinate>
                  <hot>proved</hot>
                  <crossref>
                     <theorem.ref theoremID="Thm_BasisRowColumnSpace"/>
                     <info>
                        <para>
                           <para.body>Look up this theorem.</para.body>
                        </para>
                     </info>
                  </crossref>
               </subordinate> that <math>
                  <latex>\Rnk{ \Mtrx{A} } = \Dim{ \RowSp{ \Mtrx{A} } } = \Dim{ \ColSp{ \Mtrx{ A } } }</latex>
               </math>, which implies the second and the third identity.
		</para.body>
         </para>
      </proof.block>
   </proof>
</theorem>
